questions_answers.question: What is the relationship between ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler and Fooocus?
questions_answers.answer: ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler is derived from Fooocus and has only one change: replacing the TAESD previewer in `core.py` with the standard one.

questions_answers.question: What modules are included in ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler?
What specific change was made to the ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler version?
questions_answers.answer: The only change made to the ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler version was replacing the TAESD previewer in `core.py` with the standard one.

questions_answers.question: What is the primary difference between Fooocus and ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler with respect to the previewer?
questions_answers.answer: The primary difference is that ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler uses a standard previewer instead of the TAESD previewer found in Fooocus.

questions_answers.question: Where can I find information about the changes made to ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler?
questions_answers.answer: Information about the changes made to ComfyUI_Fooocus_KSampler can be found in the GitHub repository of Fooocus at [https://github.com/lllyasviel/Fooocus](https://github.com/lllyasviel/Fooocus).
